{
  "stem": "10839.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was not married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was maybe 10 children-- sister-in-laws, two sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I got, two sisters and one brother, who were [INAUDIBLE] this time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then from the beginning, it was not so good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because my, my mother was very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She got cancer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I start-- and they told me, you are the only man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What you have to see to it to, to take care of the children, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because the women, they could not help themselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Say what, I can take care-- to hide them, to save them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I, I promise I'll do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't help myself, [PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] because I, I mentioned the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, OK, then first of all, I got to make a living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I, I took in a machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was working to make some money, to make a living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then whatever I can, I'll do for you, for the-- I mean, for their nephew and nieces.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only later on, you know, at home in this time, was the-- they made always a [INAUDIBLE], a committee, and joined with a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Jewish, we say, [HEBREW SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they, the, the Nazis, did that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And have-- they will tell them what they have to do-- they want to-- they say something to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The, the committee, they have to be the leaders and to tell the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anything what they will want, they have to, to obey the orders and to tell them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I was to have somebody there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
